dmca.title: SEO Image sends takedown to competitor
dmca.body:
Dear Google Customer Support Professionals,

1)	The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears on: http://www.seoimage.com/

2)	Search Query: 
"SEO Company" 
http://www.google.com/search?q=seo%20company&sourceid=grroowe&ie=utf-8&oe=utf-8

Infringing Web Pages: http://india-seo.indiabook.com/
1)	The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears on: http://www.seoimage.com/link_popularity.html

2)	Search Query:
"link building services"
http://www.google.com/search?g=link%20building%20services&sourceid=groowe&ie=utf-8&oe=utf-8
Infringing Web Pages:
 http://india-seo.indiabook.com/link-building-services-india.html
1)	The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears on: http://www.seoimage.com/search engine methodology.html
2)	Search Term
 "SEO Image LLC will have our copywriter optimize the text for your site"
Infringing Web Pages: 
http://india-seo.indiabook.com/search-engine-optimization-india.html
1) The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears on: http://www.seoimage.com/seo_services.html
 

2)	"We have found proven design and coding methods for staying on the top of the search engines"

http://india-seo.indiabook.com/india-seo-services.html


3)	My Contact Information: [private]@seoimage.com 
[private] (cell)

[private]
Chandigarh
null,160036

6)	I swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is accurate and that I am the copyright owner or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.

Sincerely,


[private] CEO SEO Image LLC
